---
---

<section class="policy-grid-section section-padding" id="issues">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label animate-in" style="text-align:center;display:block;" data-i18n="issues.grid_label">The Issues</span>
    <h2 class="section-title animate-in" style="text-align:center;" data-i18n="issues.grid_headline">Where Byron Stands</h2>

    <div class="policy-grid">
      <!-- Housing -->
      <div class="policy-block animate-in" id="housing">
        <div class="policy-icon-wrap">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/>
            <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="policy-title" data-i18n="issues.housing_title">Housing as a Human Right</h3>
        <ul class="policy-list">
          <li class="policy-item" data-i18n="issues.housing_1">Fight for rent stabilization and lift the ban on rent control in Illinois.</li>
          <li class="policy-item" data-i18n="issues.housing_2">Protect seniors and longtime residents from predatory developers and property tax spikes.</li>
          <li class="policy-item" data-i18n="issues.housing_3">Expand the Low Income Housing Trust Fund to be accessible for undocumented residents, as Byron successfully advocated for in Chicago.</li>
          <li class="policy-item" data-i18n="issues.housing_4">Continue developing community-driven affordable housing, like the 280+ unit site at 18th and Peoria.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Economic Populism -->
      <div class="policy-block animate-in" id="economic">
        <div class="policy-icon-wrap">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/>
            <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="policy-title" data-i18n="issues.economic_title">Economic Populism &amp; Labor Rights</h3>
        <ul class="policy-list">
          <li class="policy-item" data-i18n="issues.economic_1">Implement a LaSalle Street tax to ensure the wealthiest financial institutions pay their fair share, ending the subsidy paid by working families.</li>
          <li class="policy-item" data-i18n="issues.economic_2">Establish a public bank to give small businesses and residents fair access to credit.</li>
          <li class="policy-item" data-i18n="issues.economic_3">Stand with unionizing workers, including direct support for Amazon distribution workers demanding humane conditions.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Education -->
      <div class="policy-block animate-in" id="education">
        <div class="policy-icon-wrap">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/>
            <path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="policy-title" data-i18n="issues.education_title">Fully Funded Public Education</h3>
        <ul class="policy-list">
          <li class="policy-item" data-i18n="issues.education_1">Stand uncompromisingly with the Chicago Teachers Union and fight for a fully funded, democratically elected school board.</li>
          <li class="policy-item" data-i18n="issues.education_2">Bring federal dollars to neighborhood schools, expanding on Byron's record of securing over $1 million in infrastructure improvements for schools like Benito Juarez Community Academy.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Environmental Justice -->
      <div class="policy-block animate-in" id="environment">
        <div class="policy-icon-wrap">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 22c5.523 0 10-4.477 10-10S17.523 2 12 2 2 6.477 2 12s4.477 10 10 10z"/>
            <path d="M2 12h20"/>
            <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="policy-title" data-i18n="issues.environment_title">Environmental Justice</h3>
        <ul class="policy-list">
          <li class="policy-item" data-i18n="issues.environment_1">Hold toxic polluters accountable for environmental racism in working-class communities, continuing the fight against disasters like the Hilco implosion and MAT Asphalt.</li>
          <li class="policy-item" data-i18n="issues.environment_2">Reopen the Department of the Environment to institutionalize climate change resiliency and address public health crises like asthma and heart disease.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Public Safety -->
      <div class="policy-block policy-block-wide animate-in" id="safety">
        <div class="policy-icon-wrap">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="policy-title" data-i18n="issues.safety_title">Public Safety &amp; Human Rights</h3>
        <ul class="policy-list">
          <li class="policy-item" data-i18n="issues.safety_1">Implement community-driven, block-by-block interventions to address the root causes of violence, rather than relying on failed status-quo models.</li>
          <li class="policy-item" data-i18n="issues.safety_2">Ensure Chicago remains a reproductive health sanctuary city and expand funding for LGBTQIA+ inclusive social services.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .policy-grid-section {
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .policy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .policy-block {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    border-top: 4px solid var(--blue);
    transition: transform var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-default), box-shadow var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-default);
  }

  .policy-block:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .policy-block-wide {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  .policy-icon-wrap {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(5, 173, 237, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .policy-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .policy-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    list-style: none;
  }

  .policy-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 24px;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-700);
  }

  .policy-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 8px;
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    background: var(--orange);
    border-radius: 2px;
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .policy-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .policy-block-wide {
      grid-column: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
